**To create a placement group**

The following ``create-placement-group`` example creates a placement group with the specified name and strategy. ::

    aws ec2 create-placement-group \
        --group-name my-cluster \
        --strategy cluster

Output::

    {
        "PlacementGroup": {
            "GroupName": "my-cluster",
            "State": "available",
            "Strategy": "cluster",
            "GroupId": "pg-0abcdef1234567890",
            "Tags": []
        }
    }
